# Smart Parking Lot - Low Level Design

## Problem Statement

Design the backend of a Smart Parking Lot capable of:

- Parking Spot Allocation
- Vehicle Entry & Exit
- Fee Calculation
- Real-Time Spot Availability

---

## Functional Requirements

- Vehicle Entry
- Vehicle Exit
- Automatic Spot Allocation
- Parking Fee Calculation
- Live Spot Availability

---

## UML Class Diagram

![Class Diagram](images/ClassDiagram.png)

---

## Relationships

| Parent | Child | Relationship |
|---------|--------|--------------|
| Vehicle | Car | Inheritance |
| Vehicle | Motorcycle | Inheritance |
| Vehicle | Bus | Inheritance |
| ParkingLot | ParkingFloor | Composition |
| ParkingFloor | ParkingSpot | Composition |
| ParkingTicket | Vehicle | Aggregation |
| ParkingTicket | ParkingSpot | Aggregation |
| ParkingController | ParkingLot | Association |
| FeeService | FeeStrategy | Dependency |

---

## Design Patterns Used

- Strategy Pattern
- Factory Pattern
- Singleton Pattern
- Repository Pattern

---

## Database Design

- Vehicle
- Parking Spot
- Parking Ticket

---

## API Design

POST /checkin

POST /checkout

GET /availability
